    image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMTYiIGhlaWdodD0iMTYiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxNiAxNiIgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj4KPHBhdGggZD0iTTQgNkw4IDEwTDEyIDYiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzc1NzU3NSIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIyIiBzdHJva2UtbGluZWNhcD0icm91bmQiIHN0cm9rZS1saW5lam9pbj0icm91bmQiLz4KPC9zdmc+);
}

QComboBox QAbstractItemView {
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    selection-background-color: #e3f2fd;
}

/* Spin Boxes */
QSpinBox, QDoubleSpinBox {
    border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
}

QSpinBox:focus, QDoubleSpinBox:focus {
    border-color: #1976d2;
}

/* Date Edit */
QDateEdit {
    border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
}

QDateEdit:focus {
    border-color: #1976d2;
}

/* Group Boxes */
QGroupBox {
    font-weight: bold;
    border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 16px;  /* Increased from 1ex to prevent overlap */
    padding-top: 20px;  /* Increased from 10px for better spacing */
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    padding-left: 10px;
    padding-right: 10px;
}

QGroupBox::title {
    subcontrol-origin: margin;
    subcontrol-position: top left;
    padding: 4px 12px;  /* Increased padding for better visual separation */
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    color: #424242;
    font-size: 10pt;  /* Slightly larger font for section headers */
    margin-left: 8px;  /* Add left margin to align with content */
}

/* Tables */
QTableWidget {
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    alternate-background-color: #f9f9f9;
    gridline-color: #e0e0e0;
    selection-background-color: #e3f2fd;
}

QTableWidget::item {
    padding: 8px;
    border: none;
}

QTableWidget::item:selected {
    background-color: #e3f2fd;
    color: #1976d2;
}

QHeaderView::section {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    padding: 8px;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-right: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #424242;
}

QHeaderView::section:hover {
    background-color: #e0e0e0;
}

/* Scrollbars */
QScrollBar:vertical {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    width: 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
}

QScrollBar::handle:vertical {
    background: #c0c0c0;
    border-radius: 6px;
    min-height: 20px;
}

QScrollBar::handle:vertical:hover {
    background: #a0a0a0;
}

QScrollBar:horizontal {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
}

QScrollBar::handle:horizontal {
    background: #c0c0c0;
    border-radius: 6px;
    min-width: 20px;
}

QScrollBar::handle:horizontal:hover {
    background: #a0a0a0;
}

/* Progress Bars */
QProgressBar {
    border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
}

QProgressBar::chunk {
    background-color: #1976d2;
    border-radius: 2px;
}

/* Status Bar */
QStatusBar {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
}

/* Menu Bar */
QMenuBar {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
}

QMenuBar::item {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background: transparent;
}

QMenuBar::item:selected {
    background-color: #e3f2fd;
    color: #1976d2;
}

/* Menus */
QMenu {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    padding: 4px;
}

QMenu::item {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    margin: 2px;
}

QMenu::item:selected {
    background-color: #e3f2fd;
    color: #1976d2;
}

QMenu::separator {
    height: 1px;
    background-color: #e0e0e0;
    margin: 4px 8px;
}

/* Tool Bar */
QToolBar {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border: none;
    spacing: 4px;
    padding: 4px;
}

QToolBar::separator {
    background-color: #e0e0e0;
    width: 1px;
    margin: 4px 2px;
}

/* Tabs */
QTabWidget::pane {
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    background-color: #ffffff;
}

QTabBar::tab {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    margin-right: 2px;
}

QTabBar::tab:selected {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-bottom-color: #ffffff;
    color: #1976d2;
    font-weight: bold;
}

QTabBar::tab:hover {
    background-color: #e0e0e0;
}

/* Checkboxes */
QCheckBox {
    spacing: 8px;
}

QCheckBox::indicator {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border: 2px solid #757575;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
}

QCheckBox::indicator:checked {
    background-color: #1976d2;
    border-color: #1976d2;
    image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMTIiIGhlaWdodD0iMTIiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxMiAxMiIgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj4KPHBhdGggZD0iTTEwIDNMNC41IDguNUwyIDYiIHN0cm9rZT0id2hpdGUiIHN0cm9rZS13aWR0aD0iMiIgc3Ryb2tlLWxpbmVjYXA9InJvdW5kIiBzdHJva2UtbGluZWpvaW49InJvdW5kIi8+Cjwvc3ZnPg==);
}

QCheckBox::indicator:hover {
    border-color: #1976d2;
}

/* Radio Buttons */
QRadioButton {
    spacing: 8px;
}

QRadioButton::indicator {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border: 2px solid #757575;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
}

QRadioButton::indicator:checked {
    background-color: #1976d2;
    border-color: #1976d2;
}

QRadioButton::indicator:hover {
    border-color: #1976d2;
}

/* Splitters */
QSplitter::handle {
    background-color: #e0e0e0;
}

QSplitter::handle:horizontal {
    width: 4px;
}

QSplitter::handle:vertical {
    height: 4px;
}

QSplitter::handle:hover {
    background-color: #bdbdbd;
}

/* Dialog Buttons */
QDialogButtonBox {
    padding: 8px;
}

QDialogButtonBox QPushButton {
    min-width: 80px;
}

/* Frame styles */
QFrame[frameShape="4"] { /* StyledPanel */
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
}

QFrame[frameShape="1"] { /* Box */
    border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 4px;
}

/* Dark theme support */
QWidget[theme="dark"] {
    background-color: #2b2b2b;
    color: #ffffff;
}

QWidget[theme="dark"] QLineEdit,
QWidget[theme="dark"] QTextEdit,
QWidget[theme="dark"] QComboBox {
    background-color: #3c3c3c;
    border-color: #555555;
    color: #ffffff;
}

QWidget[theme="dark"] QPushButton {
    background-color: #0d7377;
}

QWidget[theme="dark"] QPushButton:hover {
    background-color: #14a085;
}

/* Validation styles */
QLineEdit[validation="error"] {
    border-color: #d32f2f;
    background-color: #ffebee;
}

QLineEdit[validation="success"] {
    border-color: #388e3c;
    background-color: #e8f5e8;
}

/* Loading animations */
@keyframes spin {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

QLabel[loading="true"] {
    animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
}